                     <div class=section>
                         <div class=sectname>COMMENTS</div>
                         <div class=sectbody>
                             
                                 <div class=sectline>a(n), n &gt; 0, is a multiple of 3 by symmetry. - <a href="/wiki/User:Michael_S._Branicky">Michael S. Branicky</a>, Jul 21 2021</div>
                             
                         </div>
