                     <div class=section>
                         <div class=sectname>LINKS</div>
                         <div class=sectbody>
                             
                                 <div class=sectline>Hans Havermann, <a href="/A006156/b006156.txt">Table of n, a(n) for n = 0..110</a> [Terms 1-90 come from The Entropy of Square-Free Words by Baake, Elser, &amp; Grimm (pages 10, 11). Terms 91-110 come from Grimm's Improved Bounds on the Number of Ternary Square-Free Words (page 3).]</div>
                             
                                 <div class=sectline>M. Baake, V. Elser and U. Grimm, <a href="https://arxiv.org/abs/math-ph/9809010">The entropy of square-free words</a>, arXiv:math-ph/9809010, 1998.</div>
                             
